    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Al-le-lu--i--a, al-le-lu----i----a, al-------le--lu----i---a.__\n\nIn Thee, O Lord, have I hoped, let me not be put to shame in__ the age_____ to__ come.\n\nAl-le-lu--i--a, al-le-lu----i----a, al-------le--lu----i---a.__\n\nBe Thou un-to me a God to de-fend me and a house of ref-uge___ to save me.__\n\nAl-le-lu--i--a, al-le-lu----i----a, al-------le--lu----i---a.____"
